1935;;Maria Marten, or The Murder in the Red Barn;;British;;Milton Rosmer;;Tod Slaughter, Eric Portman;;horror;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maria_Marten,_or_The_Murder_in_the_Red_Barn;;William Corder seduces then murders innocent country maiden Maria Marten in the red barn before burying her body beneath the barn floor. She gets murdered because she becomes pregnant and too annoying for William.